WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 28=

00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:49.620 line:80%
Xing?

00:01:50.540 --> 00:01:51.570 line:80%
I was wondering

00:01:51.570 --> 00:01:54.490 line:80%
why the magpies
wouldn't stop chattering.

00:01:54.490 --> 00:01:56.650 line:80%
So, Miss Cai is back
with the Young Master.

00:01:58.820 --> 00:01:59.930 line:80%
We...

00:02:00.570 --> 00:02:02.420 line:80%
I understand.

00:02:02.780 --> 00:02:03.620 line:80%
Understand what?

00:02:04.290 --> 00:02:06.700 line:80%
You stormed the execution ground
for the Young Master.

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:08.180 line:80%
The whole sect already knows.

00:02:08.180 --> 00:02:09.740 line:80%
Throughout the sect,

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:11.210 line:80%
everyone admires you.

00:02:11.650 --> 00:02:13.930 line:80%
They all say you're bold and decisive,

00:02:13.930 --> 00:02:15.810 line:80%
born to be one of us.

00:02:16.340 --> 00:02:17.860 line:80%
We've all agreed

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:19.490 line:80%
you are our future lady.

00:02:19.490 --> 00:02:20.740 line:80%
What lady?

00:02:20.740 --> 00:02:21.810 line:80%
That's nonsense.

00:02:22.060 --> 00:02:23.300 line:80%
I'm not making it up.

00:02:23.740 --> 00:02:25.300 line:80%
Elder Yan agrees too.

00:02:27.620 --> 00:02:28.530 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:02:28.530 --> 00:02:29.580 line:80%
After Nie Zhe returned,

00:02:29.900 --> 00:02:31.300 line:80%
Elder Yan scolded him

00:02:31.490 --> 00:02:32.860 line:80%
in front of everyone,

00:02:33.340 --> 00:02:35.530 line:80%
saying he nearly ruined
the sect's foundation.

00:02:35.930 --> 00:02:37.580 line:80%
He couldn't kill Elder Yan,

00:02:37.580 --> 00:02:40.140 line:80%
so he locked him back
in the Jiuzhou Archive.

00:02:40.140 --> 00:02:42.210 line:80%
That does sound like Elder Yan.

00:02:42.210 --> 00:02:43.810 line:80%
Young Master, you may not know.

00:02:43.810 --> 00:02:44.650 line:80%
Nie...

00:02:47.780 --> 00:02:48.620 line:80%
Xing,

00:02:49.410 --> 00:02:52.180 line:80%
let the Young Master
and Miss Cai wash up first.

00:02:52.580 --> 00:02:53.769 line:80%
We'll talk about anything else

00:02:53.780 --> 00:02:54.620 line:80%
in the village.

00:02:56.530 --> 00:02:57.370 line:80%
Right.

00:02:57.860 --> 00:02:59.210 line:80%
Mr. and Mrs. Mu,

00:02:59.210 --> 00:03:00.090 line:80%
come with us.

00:03:00.170 --> 00:03:01.020 line:80%
Let's go.

00:03:01.020 --> 00:03:02.410 line:80%
Aren't you going to explain?

00:03:02.860 --> 00:03:03.700 line:80%
Explain what?

00:03:04.410 --> 00:03:05.250 line:80%
We...

00:03:06.930 --> 00:03:07.770 line:80%
Forget it.

00:03:28.460 --> 00:03:30.530 line:80%
You Guanyue is shameless.

00:03:31.060 --> 00:03:33.300 line:80%
Once he heard of the capture,
he defected to Nie Zhe.

00:03:33.650 --> 00:03:34.796 line:80%
I cut ties with him long ago.

00:03:35.860 --> 00:03:37.020 line:80%
Don't worry, Young Master.

00:03:37.490 --> 00:03:39.340 line:80%
Everyone's heart is with you.

00:03:39.930 --> 00:03:42.460 line:80%
Though you haven't led the sect
for long,

00:03:42.460 --> 00:03:43.490 line:80%
you've truly done

00:03:43.490 --> 00:03:44.530 line:80%
a lot for us.

00:03:45.460 --> 00:03:47.020 line:80%
We've all been hoping for your return.

00:03:47.860 --> 00:03:49.300 line:80%
He's done a lot?

00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:50.780 line:80%
Yes.

00:03:51.090 --> 00:03:52.650 line:80%
The Young Master exempted our taxes

00:03:52.650 --> 00:03:54.910 line:80%
and allowed us to travel freely
in the Hanhai Mountains.

00:03:55.410 --> 00:03:57.250 line:80%
Otherwise, how could Grandfather
and I go out?

00:04:01.020 --> 00:04:01.860 line:80%
Young Master,

00:04:02.180 --> 00:04:03.780 line:80%
when will you reclaim Bliss Palace?

00:04:06.810 --> 00:04:07.650 line:80%
Wait a little longer.

00:04:09.090 --> 00:04:09.970 line:80%
Listen to me rambling.

00:04:10.460 --> 00:04:11.930 line:80%
The Young Master is still injured.

00:04:12.810 --> 00:04:15.090 line:80%
Uncle Xue should be back
with the herbs soon.

00:04:15.090 --> 00:04:15.970 line:80%
Village Chief.

00:04:16.580 --> 00:04:17.580 line:80%
Speak of the devil.

00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:20.410 line:80%
I brought back every herb I could find.

00:04:20.410 --> 00:04:21.382 line:80%
- Give it to me.
- Xing.

00:04:21.393 --> 00:04:22.913 line:80%
- I'll go dry them.
- Sure.

00:04:24.940 --> 00:04:25.810 line:80%
Uncle Xue.

00:04:25.830 --> 00:04:26.970 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:04:26.970 --> 00:04:27.820 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:04:28.090 --> 00:04:29.020 line:80%
Yes.

00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:29.900 line:80%
Well.

00:04:29.900 --> 00:04:30.820 line:80%
This is...?

00:04:35.290 --> 00:04:36.130 line:80%
Zhengyang?

00:04:39.580 --> 00:04:40.420 line:80%
What relation

00:04:41.050 --> 00:04:42.170 line:80%
are you to Zhengyang?

00:04:42.940 --> 00:04:44.170 line:80%
If I'm not mistaken,

00:04:44.820 --> 00:04:46.340 line:80%
the person you mentioned

00:04:46.850 --> 00:04:48.050 line:80%
should be his uncle,

00:04:48.580 --> 00:04:49.420 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang.

00:04:59.500 --> 00:05:01.170 line:80%
She was the best girl in the world.

00:05:01.900 --> 00:05:03.170 line:80%
Her heart is pure

00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:05.580 line:80%
like a clear sky.

00:05:06.410 --> 00:05:08.140 line:80%
Which family was she from?

00:05:08.140 --> 00:05:09.020 line:80%
What was her name?

00:05:10.020 --> 00:05:11.050 line:80%
Her name is

00:05:11.380 --> 00:05:12.220 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:16.570 line:80%
She gave me

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:18.700 line:80%
this wrist guard.

00:05:23.090 --> 00:05:25.730 line:80%
Did Mu Zhengyang truly love that girl?

00:05:25.730 --> 00:05:26.570 line:80%
Of course.

00:05:27.140 --> 00:05:29.730 line:80%
Zhengyang would've given her
his very heart.

00:05:30.170 --> 00:05:31.283 line:80%
When he came back that time,

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:32.410 line:80%
he said

00:05:32.410 --> 00:05:34.580 line:80%
Pingshu had agreed to marry him.

00:05:34.850 --> 00:05:36.170 line:80%
Once he finished his great cause,

00:05:36.170 --> 00:05:37.820 line:80%
he'd choose an auspicious day to wed.

00:05:38.700 --> 00:05:39.540 line:80%
He even said

00:05:39.900 --> 00:05:41.900 line:80%
he'd bring her to meet me.

00:05:43.530 --> 00:05:44.370 line:80%
But

00:05:45.140 --> 00:05:46.290 line:80%
after that,

00:05:47.650 --> 00:05:49.140 line:80%
I never saw him again.

00:05:55.140 --> 00:05:56.500 line:80%
He's gone.

00:05:59.340 --> 00:06:00.180 line:80%
Actually,

00:06:01.380 --> 00:06:02.780 line:80%
I had already guessed.

00:06:03.380 --> 00:06:04.290 line:80%
I just

00:06:04.290 --> 00:06:05.170 line:80%
had no confirmation

00:06:06.140 --> 00:06:07.460 line:80%
and didn't want to face it.

00:06:10.380 --> 00:06:11.220 line:80%
By the way,

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:14.700 line:80%
Pingshu...

00:06:17.210 --> 00:06:18.500 line:80%
She's gone too.

00:06:19.780 --> 00:06:20.620 line:80%
Life

00:06:21.580 --> 00:06:22.530 line:80%
is too unpredictable.

00:06:23.340 --> 00:06:25.850 line:80%
If Zhengyang hadn't gone
to do that great cause

00:06:26.210 --> 00:06:28.500 line:80%
and had chosen to marry Pingshu instead,

00:06:31.020 --> 00:06:32.580 line:80%
how wonderful that would've been.

00:06:47.820 --> 00:06:49.353 line:80%
The great cause Mu Zhengyang mentioned

00:06:50.580 --> 00:06:51.970 line:80%
must have been to reclaim

00:06:51.970 --> 00:06:54.090 line:80%
the Chief position
taken by Nie Hengcheng.

00:07:02.170 --> 00:07:03.380 line:80%
I don't understand.

00:07:04.610 --> 00:07:06.530 line:80%
If Mu Zhengyang truly loved my aunt

00:07:07.340 --> 00:07:09.020 line:80%
and had a feud with Nie Hengcheng,

00:07:11.140 --> 00:07:13.410 line:80%
why would he kill her close friends

00:07:13.940 --> 00:07:15.610 line:80%
and leave her to fight Nie alone?

00:07:20.700 --> 00:07:22.730 line:80%
I planned to find out
who the man in black is.

00:07:23.970 --> 00:07:25.140 line:80%
After killing Nie Zhe,

00:07:26.530 --> 00:07:28.020 line:80%
I'd seal the Youming Path,

00:07:29.090 --> 00:07:30.170 line:80%
restrain the sect members,

00:07:30.780 --> 00:07:32.730 line:80%
and prevent further conflict
with the Six Sects.

00:07:33.460 --> 00:07:34.300 line:80%
That way,

00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.210 line:80%
I could marry you openly and honorably.

00:07:58.850 --> 00:07:59.850 line:80%
But now,

00:08:00.970 --> 00:08:02.216 line:80%
I don't want to wait any longer.

00:08:04.020 --> 00:08:05.210 line:80%
I'm afraid of losing you.

00:08:09.850 --> 00:08:10.690 line:80%
Zhao,

00:08:12.460 --> 00:08:13.340 line:80%
let's get married.

00:08:50.500 --> 00:08:51.340 line:80%
Aunt.

00:09:01.860 --> 00:09:02.700 line:80%
Zhao.

00:09:17.810 --> 00:09:19.450 line:80%
The skin-painted demon.

00:10:10.810 --> 00:10:12.220 line:80%
Those people from the Six Sects

00:10:12.220 --> 00:10:13.060 line:80%
are nothing to fear.

00:10:13.710 --> 00:10:14.620 line:80%
That's good.

00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:15.460 line:80%
Shisan?

00:10:17.140 --> 00:10:18.140 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:10:18.450 --> 00:10:20.350 line:80%
Wasn't it said Nie Zhe seized power,

00:10:20.740 --> 00:10:23.170 line:80%
and you were injured
and fled with Uncle Cheng?

00:10:23.570 --> 00:10:24.450 line:80%
I am unharmed.

00:10:25.500 --> 00:10:26.740 line:80%
Uncle Cheng heard the news

00:10:26.740 --> 00:10:28.340 line:80%
and sent me to protect the Young Master

00:10:28.351 --> 00:10:29.010 line:80%
and you.

00:10:31.140 --> 00:10:32.039 line:80%
Good that you're fine.

00:10:34.410 --> 00:10:35.303 line:80%
At the market outside,

00:10:35.314 --> 00:10:36.980 line:80%
there were a few spies
from the Six Sects.

00:10:36.980 --> 00:10:38.620 line:80%
Did you run into them on your way here?

00:10:38.620 --> 00:10:39.530 line:80%
They should be gone.

00:10:42.620 --> 00:10:43.500 line:80%
Where is Mu Qingyan?

00:11:06.900 --> 00:11:08.050 line:80%
Thanks to your snow lotus,

00:11:08.926 --> 00:11:10.979 line:80%
the Cold Spirit Powder poison
in my body has eased.

00:11:11.220 --> 00:11:12.060 line:80%
In that case,

00:11:12.780 --> 00:11:14.050 line:80%
I can return with peace of mind.

00:11:15.020 --> 00:11:15.860 line:80%
Return?

00:11:19.290 --> 00:11:20.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:11:21.290 --> 00:11:22.856 line:80%
I know you're worried
about your master

00:11:23.330 --> 00:11:24.170 line:80%
and your parents

00:11:24.483 --> 00:11:25.749 line:80%
and want to go back to see them.

00:11:26.140 --> 00:11:26.980 line:80%
How about this?

00:11:27.500 --> 00:11:28.933 line:80%
Once the Six Sects stop pursuing us,

00:11:29.450 --> 00:11:30.410 line:80%
I'll go back with you.

00:11:33.900 --> 00:11:35.170 line:80%
It's been days.

00:11:36.377 --> 00:11:37.723 line:80%
They should've calmed down by now.

00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:41.900 line:80%
Just as you expected.

00:11:42.530 --> 00:11:43.620 line:80%
Just as I expected?

00:11:48.780 --> 00:11:49.690 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:11:50.330 --> 00:11:52.290 line:80%
Before entering the Hanhai Mountains,

00:11:52.290 --> 00:11:54.810 line:80%
I noticed
the Six Sects' pursuers dwindling.

00:11:56.050 --> 00:11:56.930 line:80%
Only today

00:11:57.500 --> 00:11:58.410 line:80%
did I confirm

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:00.570 line:80%
they withdrew.

00:12:02.100 --> 00:12:04.570 line:80%
What method could make

00:12:05.170 --> 00:12:08.020 line:80%
the Six Sects abandon the hunt?

00:12:10.410 --> 00:12:12.050 line:80%
Did you seize their families?

00:12:14.530 --> 00:12:15.410 line:80%
Whom did you capture?

00:12:16.740 --> 00:12:17.780 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi?

00:12:35.650 --> 00:12:36.530 line:80%
Xinrou,

00:12:36.530 --> 00:12:37.370 line:80%
rest assured.

00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:38.860 line:80%
I've informed my mother.

00:12:39.290 --> 00:12:40.410 line:80%
I'll formally marry you soon.

00:12:40.810 --> 00:12:41.860 line:80%
Those rumors

00:12:42.100 --> 00:12:43.220 line:80%
will vanish

00:12:43.780 --> 00:12:45.450 line:80%
once we wed.

00:12:55.380 --> 00:12:56.220 line:80%
What's going on?

00:12:59.050 --> 00:12:59.890 line:80%
Mr. Zhou,

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:01.900 line:80%
come with me.

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:05.860 line:80%
Guangtian Sect and Siqi Sect

00:13:06.450 --> 00:13:07.900 line:80%
weren't spared either, right?

00:13:08.660 --> 00:13:12.980 line:80%
(Song Xiuzhi, Guangtian Sect)

00:13:12.980 --> 00:13:13.820 line:80%
Who?

00:13:20.810 --> 00:13:21.860 line:80%
Who are you?

00:13:28.780 --> 00:13:30.570 line:80%
Your father schemes day and night

00:13:30.570 --> 00:13:31.650 line:80%
for your sake.

00:13:31.650 --> 00:13:33.330 line:80%
Why wear that long face all day?

00:13:36.690 --> 00:13:37.530 line:80%
Mrs. Yang,

00:13:37.740 --> 00:13:38.650 line:80%
Miss Yang,

00:13:38.650 --> 00:13:39.620 line:80%
come with us.

00:13:47.290 --> 00:13:48.810 line:80%
Qingque Sect is heavily guarded

00:13:49.930 --> 00:13:50.770 line:80%
and hard to strike.

00:13:51.170 --> 00:13:53.620 line:80%
Taichu Temple is in chaos;
you have nothing to fear.

00:13:54.140 --> 00:13:55.290 line:80%
As for Luoying Valley,

00:13:58.930 --> 00:14:00.380 line:80%
whether you seize them or not

00:14:01.530 --> 00:14:02.740 line:80%
makes little difference.

00:14:04.650 --> 00:14:06.140 line:80%
Why would I do this?

00:14:07.930 --> 00:14:10.020 line:80%
This is your chain scheme,

00:14:11.140 --> 00:14:13.100 line:80%
and seizing the Six Sects' families

00:14:13.930 --> 00:14:16.050 line:80%
is the final link.

00:14:22.410 --> 00:14:23.860 line:80%
A chain scheme?

00:14:25.690 --> 00:14:27.290 line:80%
The opening move of your grand game

00:14:28.530 --> 00:14:30.290 line:80%
was to lure out Nie Zhe's remnants

00:14:30.899 --> 00:14:32.145 line:80%
and wipe them out in one sweep.

00:14:32.980 --> 00:14:34.013 line:80%
Defeating Nie Zhe is easy,

00:14:34.860 --> 00:14:37.450 line:80%
but uprooting the Nie clan's
decades-long foundation

00:14:37.930 --> 00:14:39.020 line:80%
is far harder.

00:14:39.380 --> 00:14:41.570 line:80%
Moreover, many
have feigned allegiance to you.

00:14:42.330 --> 00:14:43.620 line:80%
You can't launch a massacre.

00:14:44.380 --> 00:14:45.220 line:80%
So,

00:14:45.900 --> 00:14:46.900 line:80%
your second move

00:14:47.330 --> 00:14:48.810 line:80%
was to use yourself as bait,

00:14:49.140 --> 00:14:50.410 line:80%
enter the game personally,

00:14:51.570 --> 00:14:53.380 line:80%
come to Qingque Sect to see me,

00:14:53.380 --> 00:14:54.620 line:80%
and be captured on purpose.

00:14:58.690 --> 00:15:01.290 line:80%
That way, those hidden Nie loyalists

00:15:01.290 --> 00:15:03.810 line:80%
and the opportunistic turncoats

00:15:03.810 --> 00:15:04.740 line:80%
would expose themselves.

00:15:05.930 --> 00:15:07.203 line:80%
Nie Zhe is suspicious by nature,

00:15:08.570 --> 00:15:09.410 line:80%
and

00:15:09.620 --> 00:15:11.020 line:80%
the man in black behind him

00:15:11.620 --> 00:15:13.290 line:80%
knows the Six Sects inside out.

00:15:14.100 --> 00:15:15.690 line:80%
Without something real,

00:15:15.980 --> 00:15:17.290 line:80%
they wouldn't fall for it.

00:15:20.930 --> 00:15:22.810 line:80%
Once news of your capture spread,

00:15:23.530 --> 00:15:24.810 line:80%
they'd take the bait.

00:15:25.330 --> 00:15:26.530 line:80%
As for the final step,

00:15:27.380 --> 00:15:29.266 line:80%
you can use the hostages
in your hand to escape

00:15:29.810 --> 00:15:31.170 line:80%
and purge the sect.

00:15:31.620 --> 00:15:33.500 line:80%
Truly meticulous.

00:15:34.020 --> 00:15:35.690 line:80%
Every move is linked.

00:15:42.650 --> 00:15:44.140 line:80%
If that were true,

00:15:45.690 --> 00:15:48.220 line:80%
wouldn't I be some mighty monster?

00:15:49.050 --> 00:15:51.050 line:80%
Lord Qi often says
I'm a skin-painted demon.

00:15:52.020 --> 00:15:53.290 line:80%
It seems

00:15:53.740 --> 00:15:55.050 line:80%
you took those words to heart.

00:15:57.650 --> 00:15:59.100 line:80%
But have you thought about this?

00:15:59.330 --> 00:16:01.220 line:80%
If I wanted to seize
the Six Sects' families,

00:16:01.810 --> 00:16:03.039 line:80%
it'd take at least half a month

00:16:03.050 --> 00:16:04.330 line:80%
just to gather them.

00:16:05.290 --> 00:16:06.903 line:80%
There wouldn't be time for me to escape.

00:16:07.410 --> 00:16:08.570 line:80%
I'd still end up

00:16:08.860 --> 00:16:10.380 line:80%
with my martial arts crippled.

00:16:22.410 --> 00:16:25.570 line:80%
That was the most crucial move
in your game.

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:32.380 line:80%
You were gambling.

00:16:35.330 --> 00:16:36.530 line:80%
You were gambling

00:16:36.980 --> 00:16:38.740 line:80%
on whether I'd defy my elders

00:16:39.050 --> 00:16:40.690 line:80%
and risk everything to save you.

00:16:43.900 --> 00:16:44.740 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:16:48.170 --> 00:16:49.050 line:80%
you won.

00:16:50.380 --> 00:16:51.220 line:80%
Master,

00:16:51.530 --> 00:16:52.530 line:80%
please let him go.

00:16:55.650 --> 00:16:56.930 line:80%
From beginning to end,

00:16:58.020 --> 00:17:00.330 line:80%
everyone was within your calculations.

00:17:01.570 --> 00:17:02.500 line:80%
Even I

00:17:03.690 --> 00:17:05.420 line:80%
was just

00:17:07.290 --> 00:17:08.980 line:80%
a convenient chess piece,

00:17:09.780 --> 00:17:10.620 line:80%
right?

00:17:21.220 --> 00:17:22.180 line:80%
These herbs

00:17:22.530 --> 00:17:23.940 line:80%
will help clear

00:17:24.420 --> 00:17:25.610 line:80%
the remaining poison in you.

00:17:28.660 --> 00:17:29.500 line:80%
From now on,

00:17:31.180 --> 00:17:32.330 line:80%
take care of yourself.

00:17:50.700 --> 00:17:52.570 line:80%
I never saw you as a chess piece.

00:17:57.460 --> 00:17:58.300 line:80%
Zhao,

00:18:00.610 --> 00:18:02.130 line:80%
I know you can't bear to leave me.

00:18:02.130 --> 00:18:06.840 line:80%
♪If we never met♪

00:18:06.850 --> 00:18:08.420 line:80%
I can't bear to leave you either.

00:18:10.570 --> 00:18:12.370 line:80%
We promised to rely on each other.

00:18:13.020 --> 00:18:14.050 line:80%
You promised me.

00:18:14.660 --> 00:18:15.500 line:80%
Let go.

00:18:18.500 --> 00:18:19.340 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:18:21.540 --> 00:18:23.870 line:80%
♪We already brushed past♪

00:18:24.050 --> 00:18:25.130 line:80%
Have some respect.

00:18:33.740 --> 00:18:36.130 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:18:36.810 --> 00:18:37.650 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:18:40.860 --> 00:18:42.610 line:80%
♪Holding you and me♪

00:18:42.610 --> 00:18:46.940 line:80%
♪Life spreads without boundary♪

00:18:47.050 --> 00:18:48.330 line:80%
The Six Sects' families

00:18:49.330 --> 00:18:50.530 line:80%
are in my hands.

00:18:50.530 --> 00:18:52.900 line:80%
♪Before death♪

00:18:54.460 --> 00:18:55.700 line:80%
If you dare leave,

00:18:58.220 --> 00:18:59.420 line:80%
I'll kill them.

00:19:25.530 --> 00:19:29.590 line:80%
♪We don't have to meet again♪

00:19:30.180 --> 00:19:31.530 line:80%
If you want to save them,

00:19:31.890 --> 00:19:32.850 line:80%
come with me.

00:19:40.940 --> 00:19:41.780 line:80%
Master,

00:19:42.130 --> 00:19:43.916 line:80%
all those sent to pursue Zhao
have withdrawn.

00:19:44.090 --> 00:19:45.700 line:80%
But Mu Qingyan hasn't released them.

00:19:45.940 --> 00:19:47.220 line:80%
They're in his hands.

00:19:48.980 --> 00:19:50.290 line:80%
We can only wait.

00:19:50.290 --> 00:19:51.700 line:80%
I said long ago

00:19:51.700 --> 00:19:53.330 line:80%
we shouldn't have captured Mu Qingyan.

00:19:53.570 --> 00:19:55.020 line:80%
He's a hot potato.

00:19:55.610 --> 00:19:56.450 line:80%
Now, look.

00:19:56.610 --> 00:19:58.130 line:80%
We lost Zhao

00:19:58.500 --> 00:19:59.850 line:80%
and several young heirs.

00:20:01.050 --> 00:20:03.090 line:80%
Mu Qingyan's foundation isn't stable.

00:20:03.359 --> 00:20:05.552 line:80%
I'm certain he wouldn't wage war
against the Six Sects

00:20:05.980 --> 00:20:07.850 line:80%
or harm those families.

00:20:08.090 --> 00:20:09.500 line:80%
As for some physical suffering,

00:20:10.180 --> 00:20:11.220 line:80%
that's unavoidable.

00:20:11.890 --> 00:20:14.420 line:80%
I never imagined
Mu Qingyan's schemes ran so deep.

00:20:15.130 --> 00:20:15.970 line:80%
If Zhao

00:20:16.370 --> 00:20:18.020 line:80%
was also within his schemes...

00:20:18.020 --> 00:20:18.860 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:21.330 line:80%
Though Mu Qingyan

00:20:22.570 --> 00:20:24.020 line:80%
is skilled at disguising himself,

00:20:24.370 --> 00:20:26.180 line:80%
Zhao is exceptionally clever.

00:20:26.586 --> 00:20:27.940 line:80%
Her heart is as clear as a mirror.

00:20:27.940 --> 00:20:28.810 line:80%
She'll figure out

00:20:29.420 --> 00:20:30.500 line:80%
many things.

00:20:30.890 --> 00:20:32.460 line:80%
Once she understands,

00:20:33.290 --> 00:20:34.740 line:80%
she will return on her own.

00:21:23.810 --> 00:21:25.020 line:80%
Mu Qingyan has been captured!

00:21:43.700 --> 00:21:44.890 line:80%
It seems you

00:21:45.370 --> 00:21:46.476 line:80%
couldn't bear for me to die.

00:21:46.700 --> 00:21:47.540 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:21:48.090 --> 00:21:48.930 line:80%
you lied to me again.

00:22:01.780 --> 00:22:03.220 line:80%
Welcome, Chief.

00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:14.130 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:22:15.090 --> 00:22:17.460 line:80%
last time you hid for over a year.

00:22:17.940 --> 00:22:19.890 line:80%
Why so impatient this time?

00:22:20.330 --> 00:22:21.500 line:80%
I got a little bored waiting.

00:22:22.330 --> 00:22:23.500 line:80%
Is everyone here?

00:22:23.500 --> 00:22:24.340 line:80%
I suppose

00:22:24.940 --> 00:22:26.850 line:80%
no one would want to miss

00:22:27.500 --> 00:22:29.330 line:80%
such great merit as killing a Mu.

00:22:29.330 --> 00:22:30.170 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:22:31.180 --> 00:22:32.906 line:80%
you're infatuated
with Cai Pingshu's niece.

00:22:33.330 --> 00:22:34.850 line:80%
For personal feelings,

00:22:34.850 --> 00:22:36.490 line:80%
you've repeatedly put the sect
in danger.

00:22:36.927 --> 00:22:38.300 line:80%
You're unworthy of being the Chief.

00:22:38.460 --> 00:22:39.980 line:80%
If you surrender now,

00:22:40.700 --> 00:22:41.890 line:80%
Chief Nie is merciful.

00:22:42.130 --> 00:22:43.660 line:80%
Perhaps he'll spare your life.

00:22:48.500 --> 00:22:49.340 line:80%
Zhao,

00:22:50.180 --> 00:22:51.090 line:80%
did you hear that?

00:22:51.660 --> 00:22:53.460 line:80%
The whole world knows

00:22:53.460 --> 00:22:54.740 line:80%
I'm hopelessly in love with you.

00:22:55.570 --> 00:22:56.410 line:80%
Shut up.

00:22:57.020 --> 00:22:58.833 line:80%
Don't tell me
this was part of your plan too.

00:22:59.530 --> 00:23:00.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:23:01.610 --> 00:23:03.570 line:80%
don't you want to see us

00:23:05.050 --> 00:23:06.220 line:80%
avenge Uncle Chang?

00:23:19.890 --> 00:23:20.730 line:80%
Father.

00:23:24.980 --> 00:23:26.810 line:80%
You Guanyue. Shangguan.

00:23:28.810 --> 00:23:31.780 line:80%
So, Mr. Mu has learned

00:23:31.780 --> 00:23:33.460 line:80%
to use women and children as hostages.

00:23:33.460 --> 00:23:34.850 line:80%
Chief, you misunderstand.

00:23:34.850 --> 00:23:37.090 line:80%
I just discovered something shocking

00:23:37.090 --> 00:23:39.050 line:80%
and rushed here

00:23:39.050 --> 00:23:41.240 line:80%
to report it.

00:23:41.250 --> 00:23:42.130 line:80%
Chief,

00:23:42.130 --> 00:23:43.130 line:80%
no need to waste words.

00:23:43.130 --> 00:23:44.330 line:80%
Everything is in position.

00:23:44.660 --> 00:23:45.980 line:80%
Take your family and break out.

00:23:47.500 --> 00:23:48.530 line:80%
Mr. Yu,

00:23:48.530 --> 00:23:49.530 line:80%
no rush.

00:23:50.330 --> 00:23:51.170 line:80%
After all,

00:23:51.420 --> 00:23:52.530 line:80%
blades have no eyes.

00:23:53.090 --> 00:23:54.290 line:80%
If Mrs. Nie or your and her son

00:23:54.700 --> 00:23:56.740 line:80%
were injured...

00:23:56.740 --> 00:23:57.580 line:80%
You Guanyue,

00:23:58.220 --> 00:23:59.330 line:80%
stop your nonsense.

00:23:59.850 --> 00:24:02.460 line:80%
I've long heard that Mr. Yu and Mrs. Nie

00:24:02.460 --> 00:24:04.570 line:80%
were childhood sweethearts.

00:24:05.130 --> 00:24:06.130 line:80%
Coincidentally,

00:24:06.660 --> 00:24:08.460 line:80%
a few days ago, Elder Yan got drunk

00:24:08.740 --> 00:24:10.420 line:80%
and mentioned the Yu clan.

00:24:10.420 --> 00:24:12.180 line:80%
Their butterfly bone is distinctive.

00:24:12.180 --> 00:24:14.530 line:80%
There's a green mark along the bone,

00:24:14.530 --> 00:24:15.530 line:80%
and it's hereditary.

00:24:15.890 --> 00:24:16.730 line:80%
I wonder

00:24:17.220 --> 00:24:19.180 line:80%
whether Si'en...

00:24:19.180 --> 00:24:20.050 line:80%
You're courting death.

00:24:23.190 --> 00:24:24.090 line:80%
Chief,

00:24:24.090 --> 00:24:25.530 line:80%
You Guanyue is sowing discord.

00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:27.130 line:80%
Don't fall for it.

00:24:29.890 --> 00:24:31.050 line:80%
Was this arranged by you too?

00:24:32.090 --> 00:24:33.500 line:80%
To attack the enemy,

00:24:34.610 --> 00:24:36.090 line:80%
one must first attack the heart.

00:24:48.460 --> 00:24:49.300 line:80%
Si'en,

00:24:50.290 --> 00:24:51.290 line:80%
come to me.

00:24:51.570 --> 00:24:52.410 line:80%
Chief,

00:24:53.290 --> 00:24:54.890 line:80%
Si'en is your son.

00:24:54.890 --> 00:24:57.020 line:80%
Chief, this is their scheme
to divide us.

00:25:11.570 --> 00:25:12.420 line:80%
Chief.

00:25:12.460 --> 00:25:13.460 line:80%
Take off your clothes.

00:25:14.290 --> 00:25:16.336 line:80%
I've been loyal to the sect
and to you for decades.

00:25:16.740 --> 00:25:18.660 line:80%
Can't that outweigh his few words?

00:25:21.330 --> 00:25:22.170 line:80%
Chief.

00:25:22.780 --> 00:25:24.420 line:80%
Will you take them off or not?

00:25:25.340 --> 00:25:26.180 line:80%
Take them off.

00:25:26.180 --> 00:25:27.020 line:80%
Chief.

00:25:55.940 --> 00:25:56.780 line:80%
Chief!

00:25:57.290 --> 00:25:58.700 line:80%
There must be deceit here.

00:26:09.370 --> 00:26:11.290 line:80%
Why did you betray me?

00:26:11.290 --> 00:26:12.130 line:80%
I didn't.

00:26:12.700 --> 00:26:14.780 line:80%
You won't even acknowledge your son?

00:26:19.940 --> 00:26:20.780 line:80%
Si'en,

00:26:21.610 --> 00:26:22.700 line:80%
am I your father?

00:26:23.370 --> 00:26:24.220 line:80%
Father,

00:26:24.220 --> 00:26:25.370 line:80%
what's wrong?

00:26:25.890 --> 00:26:28.500 line:80%
I'm your son, Father.

00:26:41.940 --> 00:26:42.780 line:80%
No.

00:26:51.370 --> 00:26:52.530 line:80%
I'll kill him to make amends.

00:26:52.530 --> 00:26:53.460 line:80%
No!

00:26:53.806 --> 00:26:54.790 line:80%
Since you won't admit it,

00:26:54.801 --> 00:26:56.130 line:80%
I'll let him die before your eyes.

00:26:56.130 --> 00:26:57.330 line:80%
Don't hurt him.

00:26:58.780 --> 00:27:00.810 line:80%
He is your son.

00:27:01.420 --> 00:27:04.220 line:80%
He is your son.

00:27:05.810 --> 00:27:06.650 line:80%
Chief,

00:27:07.020 --> 00:27:08.500 line:80%
this is their scheme to divide us.

00:27:08.780 --> 00:27:10.810 line:80%
It's their scheme, Chief.

00:27:10.810 --> 00:27:11.650 line:80%
Shut up.

00:27:18.420 --> 00:27:19.780 line:80%
Since you refuse to believe me,

00:27:21.940 --> 00:27:24.020 line:80%
I'll trade my life for his.

00:27:29.290 --> 00:27:31.500 line:80%
Mother!

00:27:36.810 --> 00:27:37.890 line:80%
Mother!

00:27:38.180 --> 00:27:40.500 line:80%
My adoptive father
showed me great kindness.

00:27:41.460 --> 00:27:42.890 line:80%
If not for him,

00:27:43.780 --> 00:27:45.700 line:80%
how would I have married

00:27:46.290 --> 00:27:48.890 line:80%
a foolish and petty man like you

00:27:49.740 --> 00:27:52.020 line:80%
and suffered such humiliation?

00:27:53.050 --> 00:27:57.010 line:80%
- I only pity my son.
- Mother!

00:27:57.660 --> 00:27:59.420 line:80%
Mother!

00:28:02.090 --> 00:28:03.570 line:80%
Mother!

00:28:03.570 --> 00:28:05.460 line:80%
Don't leave me!

00:28:05.460 --> 00:28:06.370 line:80%
Mother!

00:28:06.370 --> 00:28:09.180 line:80%
Wake up! Look at me!

00:28:09.180 --> 00:28:11.460 line:80%
Don't leave me!

00:28:11.460 --> 00:28:13.570 line:80%
Today, I'll kill this brat!

00:28:13.570 --> 00:28:15.180 line:80%
Mother!

00:28:19.290 --> 00:28:21.090 line:80%
Mother!

00:28:22.370 --> 00:28:24.020 line:80%
Ruxin didn't lie to you.

00:28:24.890 --> 00:28:26.780 line:80%
That is your biological son.

00:28:26.780 --> 00:28:28.130 line:80%
Why didn't you believe her?

00:28:28.130 --> 00:28:30.370 line:80%
Why did you drive her to death?

00:28:30.370 --> 00:28:32.370 line:80%
You'd even kill your own son.

00:28:32.370 --> 00:28:34.570 line:80%
You've ruined the sect and ruined me.

00:28:35.420 --> 00:28:36.260 line:80%
Stop!

00:28:47.180 --> 00:28:48.220 line:80%
Who is the man in black?

00:28:48.850 --> 00:28:49.690 line:80%
Who?

00:28:50.660 --> 00:28:52.980 line:80%
I won't tell you.

00:28:53.890 --> 00:28:54.890 line:80%
Once I die,

00:28:55.220 --> 00:28:57.460 line:80%
the Six Sects will fall into chaos.

00:29:00.050 --> 00:29:02.530 line:80%
Sooner or later,
you'll all be buried with me.

00:29:09.530 --> 00:29:10.370 line:80%
Nie Zhe.

00:29:10.890 --> 00:29:11.730 line:80%
Nie Zhe!

00:29:11.890 --> 00:29:12.890 line:80%
Did I permit you to die?

00:29:13.570 --> 00:29:14.603 line:80%
You're not allowed to die!

00:29:14.740 --> 00:29:16.020 line:80%
You're not allowed to die!

00:29:16.020 --> 00:29:17.220 line:80%
Father!

00:29:17.220 --> 00:29:18.850 line:80%
You're not allowed to die!

00:29:18.850 --> 00:29:20.500 line:80%
Mother!

00:29:23.290 --> 00:29:25.570 line:80%
Father!

00:29:27.810 --> 00:29:29.980 line:80%
Father!

00:29:35.420 --> 00:29:37.290 line:80%
Father, Mother...

00:29:37.290 --> 00:29:38.130 line:80%
Guanyue,

00:29:38.850 --> 00:29:39.940 line:80%
issue the order at once.

00:29:39.940 --> 00:29:41.370 line:80%
Gather the men from each altar

00:29:42.420 --> 00:29:43.780 line:80%
and wipe out Nie Zhe's remnants.

00:29:43.980 --> 00:29:44.820 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:46.810 --> 00:29:47.650 line:80%
As for this child,

00:29:48.090 --> 00:29:49.420 line:80%
find him a good family.

00:29:50.050 --> 00:29:50.890 line:80%
Take him away.

00:29:50.890 --> 00:29:51.760 line:80%
Father...

00:29:51.770 --> 00:29:52.620 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:54.370 --> 00:29:56.290 line:80%
I don't want to go with you.

00:29:57.180 --> 00:29:58.050 line:80%
Father!

00:29:58.050 --> 00:29:59.330 line:80%
Mother!

00:30:00.090 --> 00:30:00.980 line:80%
Father!

00:30:00.980 --> 00:30:02.370 line:80%
Mother!

00:30:03.090 --> 00:30:05.500 line:80%
Mother!

00:30:06.700 --> 00:30:10.020 line:80%
Father!

00:30:16.330 --> 00:30:17.220 line:80%
All of this

00:30:19.090 --> 00:30:20.700 line:80%
was part of your plan.

00:30:21.420 --> 00:30:22.850 line:80%
I intended to use Yu Huiyin

00:30:23.810 --> 00:30:24.940 line:80%
to capture Nie Zhe alive

00:30:26.570 --> 00:30:28.216 line:80%
and learn
the man in black's whereabouts.

00:30:30.090 --> 00:30:31.330 line:80%
So, it means

00:30:33.020 --> 00:30:34.330 line:80%
that except for Nie Zhe's death,

00:30:35.220 --> 00:30:36.740 line:80%
everything went as you wished.

00:30:37.220 --> 00:30:38.500 line:80%
Suspicion is like wildfire.

00:30:38.980 --> 00:30:40.290 line:80%
A single spark can start a blaze.

00:30:41.740 --> 00:30:43.740 line:80%
Nie Zhe was always deeply suspicious.

00:30:45.500 --> 00:30:46.810 line:80%
Impressive tactics indeed.

00:30:47.290 --> 00:30:48.980 line:80%
Whether Yu Huiyin lived or died,

00:30:49.370 --> 00:30:50.390 line:80%
he'd surely grow estranged

00:30:51.370 --> 00:30:52.700 line:80%
from Nie Zhe after this scheme.

00:30:53.810 --> 00:30:55.420 line:80%
But why use Nie Zhe

00:30:55.420 --> 00:30:56.280 line:80%
to kill Li Ruxin?

00:30:56.280 --> 00:30:57.460 line:80%
I never meant for her to die.

00:31:05.420 --> 00:31:06.260 line:80%
Zhao,

00:31:08.530 --> 00:31:09.570 line:80%
you still don't believe me.

00:31:12.500 --> 00:31:13.940 line:80%
I don't believe you didn't foresee

00:31:13.940 --> 00:31:15.290 line:80%
this outcome.

00:31:16.570 --> 00:31:17.410 line:80%
Why?

00:31:18.660 --> 00:31:20.090 line:80%
Why do this?

00:31:21.220 --> 00:31:22.370 line:80%
Only by doing this

00:31:23.130 --> 00:31:24.570 line:80%
can black and white be separated,

00:31:25.163 --> 00:31:26.883 line:80%
and loyalty and treachery
be distinguished.

00:31:27.530 --> 00:31:28.500 line:80%
Only by doing this

00:31:28.746 --> 00:31:30.419 line:80%
can Bliss Palace
and the Hanhai Mountains,

00:31:30.430 --> 00:31:31.710 line:80%
you and I,

00:31:32.050 --> 00:31:33.460 line:80%
find true peace.

00:31:42.330 --> 00:31:43.700 line:80%
Now, everything is over.

00:31:44.500 --> 00:31:45.340 line:80%
Stay,

00:31:46.370 --> 00:31:47.210 line:80%
okay?

00:31:49.740 --> 00:31:50.700 line:80%
I don't understand.

00:31:56.850 --> 00:31:58.850 line:80%
Did you really have to go this far?

00:32:45.220 --> 00:32:50.700 line:80%
(Carefree)

00:33:05.090 --> 00:33:05.930 line:80%
Zhao.

00:33:09.660 --> 00:33:10.500 line:80%
Zhao.

00:33:40.020 --> 00:33:40.860 line:80%
Zhao.

00:34:05.610 --> 00:34:06.850 line:80%
I thought you left.

00:34:10.540 --> 00:34:11.580 line:80%
It's good you didn't.

00:34:20.780 --> 00:34:21.810 line:80%
The poison in you

00:34:22.140 --> 00:34:23.073 line:80%
must be cleared slowly.

00:34:24.290 --> 00:34:25.810 line:80%
Don't recklessly use your qi again.

00:34:26.850 --> 00:34:28.930 line:80%
I planted some blood-activating herbs.

00:34:29.740 --> 00:34:30.790 line:80%
They'll help you

00:34:30.801 --> 00:34:32.021 line:80%
dispel the poison and recover.

00:34:32.700 --> 00:34:34.660 line:80%
When you have time, brew them in water.

00:34:35.270 --> 00:34:36.770 line:80%
Add some goji berries and brown sugar.

00:34:36.970 --> 00:34:37.810 line:80%
It tastes good.

00:34:42.410 --> 00:34:43.250 line:80%
Zhao,

00:34:43.490 --> 00:34:44.410 line:80%
I'll release

00:34:45.010 --> 00:34:46.116 line:80%
all the Six Sects' families.

00:34:46.540 --> 00:34:47.490 line:80%
Except for Nie Zhe,

00:34:47.490 --> 00:34:48.863 line:80%
I'll give everyone a proper burial.

00:34:49.580 --> 00:34:50.780 line:80%
Once the purge is finished,

00:34:51.410 --> 00:34:52.930 line:80%
I'll order the Youming Path sealed.

00:34:53.850 --> 00:34:54.930 line:80%
We'll stay here forever

00:34:56.010 --> 00:34:56.970 line:80%
and never part again,

00:34:58.060 --> 00:34:58.900 line:80%
okay?

00:35:03.220 --> 00:35:04.060 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:35:05.370 --> 00:35:06.620 line:80%
Uncle Cheng just said

00:35:06.970 --> 00:35:08.290 line:80%
Xue Youfu needs me.

00:35:09.620 --> 00:35:10.660 line:80%
I'll go over first.

00:35:39.660 --> 00:35:40.700 line:80%
Fire starter.

00:35:45.930 --> 00:35:46.770 line:80%
Bamboo hat.

00:35:49.410 --> 00:35:50.490 line:80%
Straw raincoat.

00:35:51.660 --> 00:35:52.970 line:80%
You don't know.

00:35:52.970 --> 00:35:55.060 line:80%
Every altar is clearing out
the Nie remnants.

00:35:55.060 --> 00:35:56.330 line:80%
It's chaotic.

00:35:56.330 --> 00:35:57.545 line:80%
Those tied to Nie Zhe

00:35:57.556 --> 00:35:58.780 line:80%
are fleeing one after another.

00:35:58.780 --> 00:36:00.290 line:80%
These items are selling fast.

00:36:00.290 --> 00:36:01.290 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:36:01.290 --> 00:36:02.370 line:80%
I saved a set just for you.

00:36:04.780 --> 00:36:05.660 line:80%
Thank you, Uncle Xue.

00:36:07.140 --> 00:36:09.700 line:80%
The Young Master just let them leave?

00:36:09.930 --> 00:36:11.290 line:80%
I heard from Master You

00:36:11.780 --> 00:36:14.140 line:80%
that he won't make things hard
for those who want to go.

00:36:14.140 --> 00:36:15.879 line:80%
As long as they leave
the Hanhai Mountains,

00:36:15.890 --> 00:36:17.140 line:80%
he won't pursue them.

00:36:18.010 --> 00:36:18.970 line:80%
I also heard

00:36:20.410 --> 00:36:22.490 line:80%
he plans to seal the Youming Path

00:36:22.490 --> 00:36:24.290 line:80%
and cut off contact
with the outside world.

00:36:24.290 --> 00:36:25.130 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:36:25.540 --> 00:36:26.380 line:80%
is that true?

00:36:31.540 --> 00:36:32.740 line:80%
I'm not sure.

00:36:33.290 --> 00:36:34.290 line:80%
Uncle Xue,

00:36:34.290 --> 00:36:35.870 line:80%
if there's nothing else, I'll be going.

00:36:37.330 --> 00:36:38.220 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:36:39.700 --> 00:36:41.060 line:80%
may I ask you something?

00:36:50.620 --> 00:36:52.100 line:80%
The Pingshu

00:36:53.010 --> 00:36:54.410 line:80%
Zhengyang spoke of...

00:36:54.410 --> 00:36:56.010 line:80%
Was she your aunt,

00:36:56.660 --> 00:36:57.620 line:80%
Cai Pingshu?

00:36:59.100 --> 00:37:00.100 line:80%
You guessed.

00:37:00.410 --> 00:37:02.010 line:80%
I wasn't certain before.

00:37:02.370 --> 00:37:04.060 line:80%
But when I was packing to flee,

00:37:04.540 --> 00:37:06.380 line:80%
I found a painting
Zhengyang made while drunk.

00:37:06.890 --> 00:37:08.290 line:80%
The woman in it

00:37:08.290 --> 00:37:09.290 line:80%
has a bearing like yours.

00:37:13.700 --> 00:37:14.620 line:80%
It was my aunt.

00:37:15.700 --> 00:37:17.330 line:80%
So, it truly was Cai Pingshu.

00:37:17.330 --> 00:37:18.170 line:80%
No wonder.

00:37:18.740 --> 00:37:20.180 line:80%
Zhengyang said Pingshu

00:37:20.180 --> 00:37:21.490 line:80%
was an extraordinary woman.

00:37:25.810 --> 00:37:26.700 line:80%
Uncle Xue,

00:37:28.410 --> 00:37:29.740 line:80%
what kind of person

00:37:30.620 --> 00:37:32.140 line:80%
was Mu Zhengyang?

00:37:34.801 --> 00:37:45.461 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:38:04.221 --> 00:38:08.631 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:38:09.196 --> 00:38:13.811 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:38:14.151 --> 00:38:18.716 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:38:19.241 --> 00:38:23.541 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:38:26.486 --> 00:38:31.186 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:31.711 --> 00:38:36.001 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:36.661 --> 00:38:40.691 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:41.006 --> 00:38:46.131 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:46.706 --> 00:38:51.516 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:51.731 --> 00:38:55.901 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:56.626 --> 00:39:00.561 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:01.061 --> 00:39:06.336 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

